<style> .... </style>
    -Enables CSS into html code
    -Usually nested in the <head> tag

!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!    OR (WHICH IS BETTER!)

Use .css files
    -Must include the <style> tag

<link href="link-to-css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    -You must link your html to css sheet using this tag
    -Must be written in the head
    - link-to-css can be a url, or a relative path if style.css index.html are in the same directory
